"Hom ndzi ehurusi wɔ EWURADZE mu: "Hom mfa nsankutsen nda EWURADZE ase: Hom mfa bɛntasanku a no do ahoma du ntow no ayɛyindwom."
"Hom ntow ndwom fofor mma no; Hom mbɔ sanku yie nka dede huu ho."
"Na EWURADZE n'asɛm tsen; Na no ndwuma nyinara da no nokwardzi edzi."
"EWURADZE dɔ ndzeyɛtsenenee na atsɛntsenenee: Na n'adɔyɛ ahyɛ asaase ma."
"EWURADZE n'asɛm na ɔdze yɛɛ ɔsor; Na n'anomu ehubɔw na ɔdze yɛɛ no mu dɔm nyinara."
"Ɔka po nsu boa ano dɛ kuw: Na ɔdze n'ebun sie ekyirekyir."
"Wɔmma asaase nyinara nsuro EWURADZE: Wɔmma hɔn a wɔtse wiadze nyinara mbɔ no ho hu."

"Hom ndzi ehurusi wɔ EWURADZE mu: "EWURADZE ma amanaman egyinatu yɛ kwa: Ɔno na ɔma aman adwen yɛ gyan."
"EWURADZE n'apam gyina pintsinn daa nyina
ao hom atseneneefo Ɔfata hɔn a wɔtsen d: N'akoma mu adwen wɔ hɔ ma mbasantsen nyinara."

"Hom ndzi ehurusi wɔ EWURADZE mu: "Nhyira aka ɔman a EWURADZE yɛ hɔn Nyankopɔn; Nkorɔfo a wɔasan mu eyi hɔn ayɛ nankasa n'egyapadze no."
"EWURADZE fi sor na ɔhwɛ; Ɔhwɛ nyimpa mba nyinara;"
"Ofi ne tsenabea na ɔto n'enyi hwɛ Asaase do atsefo nyinara;"
"Ɔno na ɔbɔɔ hɔn nyinara hɔn akoma
"Ɔhen bi nndua dɔm dodow do nnya nkwa: Ɔkatakyi nndua ahoɔdzen kɛse do nngye noho."
"Ɔpɔnkɔ yɛ adze gyangyan ma nkwagye: Nkyii so ɔremmfa n'ahoɔdzen kɛse no nngye obiara."
"Hwɛ
ao hom atseneneefo Ɔfata hɔn a wɔtsen d: EWURADZE enyiwa wɔ hɔn a wosuro no do
"#Dwom 32.11": Ɔwɔ hɔn a hɔn enyi da n'adom kwan no do;"

"Hom ndzi ehurusi wɔ EWURADZE mu: "Dɛ ɔbɛgye hɔn kra efi owu mu
ao hom atseneneefo Ɔfata hɔn a wɔtsen d: Na ɔama woenya nkwa wɔ ɔkɔm mu."

"Hom ndzi ehurusi wɔ EWURADZE mu: "Hɛn akra twer EWURADZE: Ɔno na ɔyɛ hɛn boafo na hɛn kyɛm."
"Na hɛn akoma bɔtɔ hɛn yamu wɔ no mu
ao hom atseneneefo Ɔfata hɔn a wɔtsen d: Osiandɛ yɛdze hɛn werɛ ahyɛ ne dzin krɔnkrɔn no mu."

"Hom ndzi ehurusi wɔ EWURADZE mu: "EWURADZE
ao hom atseneneefo Ɔfata hɔn a wɔtsen d: ma wo mbɔbɔrhu mbra hɛn do
"#Dwom 32.11": Dɛ mbrɛ yɛdze hɛn enyi ato wo do no."
